description: A library of different .NET Standard utilities.
releaseNotes:
# Changelog

All notable changes to this package will be documented in this file.

This package adheres to [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/) and [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

Dates are in UTC-3.

## [Unreleased]

## [1.1.0] - 2019-12-16

### Added

- `StringExtensions`: Contains `ToTitleCase()`.

## [1.0.1] - 2019-12-15

### Changed

- Switched from .NET Standard 2.1 to 2.0.

## [1.0.0] - 2019-12-15

### Added

- `EventHandler` and `EventHandler<T>`: An event handler without a sender argument and its variant with a generic event args parameter.
- `Property<T>`: A wrapper around a getter and a setter.

#### Extensions

- `ArrayExtensions`: Contains `IndexOf(object element)`.
- `ObjectExtensions`: Contains `IsOneOf(params object[] objects)`.

#### Utilities

- `Utilities.IOUtilities`: Contains `ClearDirectory(string path)`, `CopyDirectory(string sourcePath, string newPath)`, `RenameDirectory(string directoryPath, string newName)` and `RenameFile(string filePath, string newName)`.
